data.description: Warm & inviting 3 bedroom/2.5 bath home in Summerlin's desirable Willows Community. An entertainer's DREAM, there are multiple living spaces, dual fireplaces downstairs, vaulted ceilings, open concept kitchen & family room, stunning yard w/ solar heated pool & waterfall, newly painted patio, & separate turfed area for your furry friends. Mature landscaping, private side garden, new water heater (7/23), XL dog door, Ring camera system throughout, custom blinds, & surround sound system in living room are some of the many great features. Large Primary bedroom w/ soaking tub, tiled shower, & dual sinks, all separate from the 2 spare bedrooms. Kitchen features black appliances, pantry, island, & custom cabinets. Privately located on a cul-de-sac, this home is mere mins from Downtown Summerlin, Ballpark, Sprouts, restaurants, & the best shopping in Summerlin! PAID OFF solar panels keep your electric bill low & your pool warm in the winter! LOW HOA for upscale Summerlin! Come see today!
